解法1：暴力解法，解法的结果是超时.

```java
class Solution {
    public int maxProfit(int[] prices) {
        int result = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i < prices.length-1; i++){
            for(int j = i+1; j < prices.length;j++){
                int temp = prices[j] - prices[i];
                if( temp > result){
                    result = temp;
                }
            }
        }
        return result;
    }
}
```

